comments.author: @dhari5551
comments.text: I'm an Inter Milan fan since I was little. For several months now I don't want to see news about Inter Milan. Because of my disappointment with the management regarding player transfers, what Inter needs they don't give. The lack of a young, good and experienced center back is not given. Lookman is a player who is predicted to be a surprise player who comes but is only a false hope for fans. I don't mean to belittle Inter Milan's current defenders, but in reality, Inter Milan really needs a young, strong center back who can match the speed of the opponent's attackers and read the game. So far in Serie A, the champions always have a strong defense. Other teams want to be champions and they are willing to sacrifice to buy good players, Inter wants to be champions but never wants to sacrifice at least to buy 1 big star player who can raise the fans' spirits.
